The school has supreme campus safty. The school respones to all student disturbances on campus. Also the school campus is strict on tresspassers
It has chapionship Mens basjetball team, along with bassbal, and soft ball. Also has a published wrting club. Along with strong international clubs.
Great for student who are unsure of what major to take. Great for student who havent been in school for years at a time. Also great for students who need help with career development.

Students have a tridition of going to the Tacoma community college v.s peirce community college rival athletic events. It has great community awearness and influence throught the city. The school has great commitment to students and staff.

Tacoma community college is a great place for students who are not sure or need more prepration for high college universities. Also a good place to develope diversity and networking. along with great althletic clubs..
Students can join music clubs, writing club, and student government clubs. Also students have acsecess to exercise facility.
Tacoma community college has great dinning and study ares for students. Also along with coffee stands, and prep cook foods, and hot served food.
Tacoma community college does not have dorms. However the school is surrounded by food stores, and living apartments.
the academics are high and heavey. course loads have havey reading and homework givien. Also great tutoring centers to help students with their studies.
Prospective students should on top of stduies from different course loads. Also awear of deadlines for applications, finacial aid enrollments. As well as the commute travel a student has to make.
On a scale of 1-10 Tacoma community college is a 9 on my judgement scale. the school has good acedemics and teaching staff. Also along with career develepment oppurtunities.
